data.description: Great four bedroom two bath home that has a side entry two car garage. This home has two guest bedrooms at the front of the home of which one could be a study or office. Two of the guest bedrooms are separated by a hall with a full bath in between.This home has a very open Living and Dining area and a very pretty kitchen that features solid wood custom cabinetry,granite counter tops microwave, free standing range and a dishwasher standard with upgrades available. All Fox Home Builder Homes will have porcelain tile except the bedrooms and closets. The Master bedroom features a sitting room area and the bath has both a walk in tiled shower and garden tub. The front yard will be sodded and landscaped.
